hledger (https://hledger.org) is:

- free, robust, friendly, fast, cross-platform, double-entry, multi-currency, multi-interface, GNU GPL accounting software
- built around human-readable, version-controllable, future-proof plain text files
- for both beginners and experts.

It is a combination of accounting app, bookkeeping multitool, bootcamp/refresher course, and supportive community.
The UIs may seem basic at first, but hledger is powerful, dependable, and fun to use.
It can help you learn bookkeeping, untangle accounting messes, track your financial status and history, 
run forecasts, set budgets and saving goals, produce detailed time reports, convert/transform financial data,
check the correctness of other systems, and create more balance and calm in your life!
If you find it valuable, consider becoming a sponsor (https://hledger.org/sponsor.html).
